Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赏月忆旧事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.56,0:00:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,观星怀往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与友人们度过的那些日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太阳只知照亮过去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.21,0:00:21.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来仍旧匿影藏形
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.33,0:00:24.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何窥视镜中世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.14,0:00:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,映出的也只是现在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:30.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.01,0:00:33.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那金灿灿的稻穗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.73,0:00:35.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩童们上扬的嘴角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.57,0:00:38.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而今至少让我酣梦一场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.16,0:00:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦至归家的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.14,0:00:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还是那么有诗意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:45.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.76,0:00:49.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嘴上一直都在说 但真的有那样一个地方么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:53.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说的那个才是幻梦吧 老师?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:59.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天真烂漫的琴 我的乖孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.88,0:01:03.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是你 一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.41,0:01:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:10.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光芒四射 至尊无上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.90,0:01:16.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再适合你不过
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.50,0:01:19.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是莫名其妙啊 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.37,0:01:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琴你可真是个笨蛋呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.36,0:01:24.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁让养我的人就这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真过分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在一个天朗气清的春季吉日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.67,0:02:08.05,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(750,300)\fad(500,10)}很\N久\N以\N前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.76,0:02:06.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明惠上人离开了喧嚣的都会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,移居到了高尾山中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:18.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他有一个烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是你们说想看我才画的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.65,0:02:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日子不好过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.81,0:02:38.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs30}真的出来一条龙呀!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.58,0:02:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看那里真的是座妖怪庙 上人真的是个妖怪啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.84,0:02:46.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然也没出什么事啦 不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.89,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(410,198)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.89,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(410,230)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.65,0:02:47.89,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(409,225)}村\N姑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:50.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定他是人狐相交的后代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,194)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,226)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,258)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,290)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.94,0:02:50.02,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,284)}带\N孩\N子\N的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:53.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上人可是十分高风亮节的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:55.12,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(440,277)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:55.12,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(440,309)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:55.12,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(439,304)}僧\N人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.53,0:02:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看他是连通阴阳之神
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.25,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,187)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.25,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,219)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.25,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs40\1c&HA8BFDE&\pos(1070,251)}■
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:59.25,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1070,244)}阴\N阳\N寮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在搞些可怕的动作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.44,0:03:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是发生什么我们很难办的——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.00,0:03:10.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不过是画能动了而已 何必大惊小怪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.73,0:03:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这么想吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.02,0:03:29.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们本以为除了忠犬 没人再理会他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.31,0:03:32.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但悄悄关注他的其实另有一物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那便是他所画的兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只名为古都的黑兔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他随手画在隔扇纸上 来做都城之神的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.21,0:03:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如愿离开都城之后 他仍未搁笔描绘幻想出的城镇与生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.78,0:03:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而它望着他的身影 似窥到了他内心深藏之物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此外 它也喜欢他帅气的脸庞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.02,0:04:05.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,螳螂捕蝉黄雀在后
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那即是佛眼佛母像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:09.07,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}佛眼佛母：为密教胎藏界曼茶罗遍知院及释迦院之一尊。\N其为生佛部功德之母，故称佛母；又具五眼，故称佛眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这尊冠有佛眼之名的菩萨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.05,0:04:16.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一眼就看穿了黑兔的心思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把身体借予你如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:24.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你的身体有太多限制了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.31,0:04:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 恐怕不会有任何进展的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:34.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这种状态下 明惠会感受到你的心意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:39.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的心上人 可是那个明惠哟!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人挺好的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:47.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明惠心中有所乖僻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛能看到未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对过去却无能为力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:05:00.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你现在心中的爱慕 正能够拯救他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:21.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是古都
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何变成了人形?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.34,0:05:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.12,0:05:33.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:34.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.64,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.19,0:05:35.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.47,0:05:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢 我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.76,0:05:49.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会在你身边 直到你明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.98,0:05:53.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.54,0:05:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:05:59.70,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\1c&HF0F0F0&\pos(60,660)}拉\N布\N拉\N多\N犬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兔子的说辞十分混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.20,0:06:08.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但二人的生活让他心中也不知不觉萌发情意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.04,0:06:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药师丸~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时光流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.70,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,270)\fn宋体\bord1.5\be1\fs40}三\N子\N\N药\N师\N丸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一同生活的人也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.83,0:06:22.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为挺好玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.53,0:06:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看不好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.37,0:06:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀哎呀 不要吵架哟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.90,0:06:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍~马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.65,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,270)\fn宋体\bord1.5\be1\fs40}长\N子\N\N鞍\N马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:41.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 红薯烤好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.58,0:06:42.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.55,0:06:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给你拿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.13,0:06:45.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.75,0:06:51.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:52.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太过分哦 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八濑~
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:07:01.10,note-black,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1150,270)\fn宋体\bord1.5\be1\fs40}二\N女\N\N八\N濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么把我画成一只鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.53,0:07:06.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快住手 八濑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以吃上人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:09.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最讨厌的就是你!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然是个古怪的家庭 但他们却很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.69,0:07:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:35.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个麻烦家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好不容易把他…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.40,0:07:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赶到山里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.94,0:07:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的面子却丢光了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.11,0:07:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫司大人!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:43.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请您定夺!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信上写的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.46,0:08:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用说得太生动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.75,0:08:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「你们家在都城是个麻烦事 叫人为难」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.74,0:08:04.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「给我解决了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全怪你吧 估计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.10,0:08:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是鞍马啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.27,0:08:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早晚会遭人口舌的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.72,0:08:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们也是有职责的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.96,0:08:22.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.73,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.45,0:08:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和八濑变回画不就好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.75,0:08:33.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药师丸本来就是人类
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有妈妈的话就能蒙混过去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们暂时消失 回头再做一次不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.80,0:08:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸你没问题的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:49.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会做的 鞍马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.05,0:09:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干脆 我们全家迁去隔扇上所画的画中世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.83,0:09:11.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 那可…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.32,0:09:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真爱你呀 古都
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.03,0:09:31.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:33.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说不要紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.78,0:09:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边的都城也叫「京」么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总得有个名字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:45.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边也叫「古都」不好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少要换个字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.50,0:09:58.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是 这一家人就移居至镜中都城
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从此便销声匿迹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.56,0:10:11.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都城由上人和古都管理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取名为镜中都城
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是人与妖共存的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.61,0:10:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.01,0:10:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公战死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还活着!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我射中的是 你那罪孽之心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.44,0:10:33.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,画中创造的东西会重生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,损坏的东西也会立刻修复
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.76,0:10:39.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.86,0:10:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:41.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家人仍然定居在住惯了的山中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们却在这广阔的庭院中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自由地玩耍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:50.19,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,220)\bord1.5\be1\fs35}鞍\N马\N寺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:51.01,note-black,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(1060,230)\bord1.5\be1\3c&HAE84D9&\fs35}八\N濑\N的\N村\N落
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你 花田 我喜欢你!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.23,0:10:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要给我生孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:57.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要回家咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这不可思议的国度
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.88,0:11:05.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生活是如此的绚烂而愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.99,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从未有任何问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:10.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都是安稳的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:18.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们不会死去 也不会新生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.78,0:11:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都按上人与古都所想而运转
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.45,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 没有纷争是好事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说除此之外你有些不满?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.23,0:11:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可没这么说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别那么认真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.30,0:11:33.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不觉得奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:39.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到何时才能长大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.95,0:11:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又让它跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:48.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可真是每天都够欢快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.57,0:11:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.87,0:11:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要能永远和妈妈在一起就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.46,0:11:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东西能修好也很方便
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候也会进来一些新东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是还有「开站」嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:01.81,note-white,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：见《京骚戏画第2弹》第3话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.54,0:12:04.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什么不满的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没什么不满啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:10.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正因为没有不满才会觉得不安吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.92,0:12:45.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.91,0:12:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又做了同一个梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去了又能怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.98,0:12:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要再变回兔子么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.72,0:12:59.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我和佛祖的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的任性…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.70,0:13:03.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间拖延至今
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:08.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然事已至此 你如此惊慌又有何用
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:14.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是画中的一只兔子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.30,0:13:18.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全凭佛祖大发慈悲 我才得以借用这人形
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.39,0:13:24.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我许诺过 一旦我对你的感情有了回报 就把身体还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.64,0:13:27.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.56,0:13:32.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…终有一天会给这世界带来不祥之物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.15,0:13:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…每当我看到你和孩子们的脸庞…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:42.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就骗自己说「再多等一天 就一天」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.06,0:13:48.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,佛眼佛母的眼是观透三千世界的真理之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.00,0:13:53.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 梦变成现实也只是时间问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:59.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道得这么透彻 却还一直装作不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.94,0:14:00.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真是恣意妄为
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.96,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.17,0:14:06.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也跟你一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.61,0:14:10.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然心里明白 却做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.26,0:14:12.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.36,0:14:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更害怕会失去你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:19.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.89,0:14:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝不会让你孤身一人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是一场突如其来的离别
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.55,0:14:43.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,双亲离去后的镜都
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.32,0:14:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们的身边 只留下了和他们在一起时的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有不知何时才能兑现的承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每天都这么不厌其烦地打过来 还真不容易
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在都没什么东西需要报告了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:29.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 烦死了!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖 听好了啊 看好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:40.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要这个吧? 想吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.81,0:15:42.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的话——
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.67,0:15:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去叼回来!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.72,0:15:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么久以前的事 亏你还记得呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的回忆里 没有一件事是该忘记的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.51,0:16:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经常被别人说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.41,0:16:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,光是身体被升级了 脑子却一点没变
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.36,0:16:17.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.14,0:16:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药师丸变得高大了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.84,0:16:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就被彻底抛在后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.68,0:16:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起明惠 叫习惯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.58,0:16:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:34.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 改变了的东西肯定有其意义
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.23,0:16:38.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是你的名字 也肯定如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.14,0:16:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过 我还是很高兴你一如既往地来找我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:17:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道啦 别这么生气嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.96,0:17:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我随便 是你们太认真!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在用心听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.76,0:17:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都说对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.84,0:17:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:21.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.73,0:17:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又偷懒没去议会?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.57,0:17:33.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们这位明惠上人 也真是不靠谱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.55,0:17:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正是个代理
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是念珠对你很重要吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是真那么讨厌 别做就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.94,0:17:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.51,0:17:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,试过啦?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.20,0:17:56.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结局很糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.48,0:18:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找时间告诉你 你肯定会笑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 念珠交给了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到他们回来之前 这里就是个梦幻国度
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs25\pos(870,675)}仙境
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.00,0:18:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不容易呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:12.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得跟自己无关一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.26,0:18:15.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你的身份差太远了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更重要的是 我喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.26,0:18:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.33,0:18:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 ~坚强可怜的明惠~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.62,0:18:28.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很辛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.13,0:18:31.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能安慰我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.12,0:18:35.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.81,0:18:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你对所有人都说这话啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没没没
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要过夜不
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.88,0:18:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.54,0:18:50.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我…睡会…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.11,0:19:01.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是某天…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:08.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出现一个能把你带离这个世界的人 那就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.52,0:19:10.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:20.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有一天 我一定会带着开始与结束回来这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.76,0:19:24.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等着我 明惠
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.30,0:19:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明惠 外面很不对劲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.37,0:19:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs35}分析结果立刻转到我这边来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.78,0:19:53.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这骚动 就好像地狱的盖子要打开了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的类比未必不对
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过打开的 也有可能是天国的门扉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.17,0:20:10.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这也想来点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:14.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁给我弄个过来?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.16,0:20:20.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鞍马 求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我送到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:24.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有! 它坏掉啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.66,0:20:26.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才来求你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么概率啊 真不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.26,0:20:32.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道啊 我也搞不清!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对 虽然只是直觉 但我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.20,0:20:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那种光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从前我和那家伙一起见过
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.15,0:20:48.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上人!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐 不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不在哦——
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 好不容易找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.78,0:21:43.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追到星球尽头我也要把你找出来!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.40,0:21:53.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小哥 你是这儿的人?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:21:57.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是神社的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.06,0:22:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没看到兔子? 黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛红红的——
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.36,0:22:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有双耳朵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.89,0:22:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有张嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.86,0:22:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有双腿呢~
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:11.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神社…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.88,0:22:13.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.62,0:22:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个偏避地头的人啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.63,0:22:22.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:28.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊 这里叫什么地方?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.00,0:22:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点 我在问你这是第几平行轴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么 这家伙不说话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.91,0:22:44.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.11,0:22:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镜中之都 镜都
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.02,0:22:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么第几平行不平行的 我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.56,0:23:01.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经几百年禁止普通人进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.77,0:23:06.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是没有监护人的普通小孩可以来玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.61,0:23:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.93,0:23:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去 尚且有许多星星混杂在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.61,0:23:19.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人与神之间的界限还很模糊的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是围绕某个家庭所发生的 爱与重生的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:26.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫琴
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.32,0:23:32.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自第一平行轴中央 统一机构 「神社」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.70,0:23:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宫司直辖部队 稻荷班
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:38.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 是来寻找监护人的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.42,0:25:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我问你们
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.56,0:25:17.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来到陌生的地方 会不会突然想起过去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.74,0:25:21.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我想起的都是些讨厌的回忆啦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.54,0:25:23.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定也会想起一点点好事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.73,0:25:29.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊~ 神社的各位现在怎么样了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.66,0:25:30.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是很寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.37,0:25:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说…不会觉得清净了许多吧?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.78,0:25:37.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 到来的是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.73,0:25:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹 闪亮登场!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
